{%- doc -%}
  Karinex Mega Menu — premium SaaS-grade navigation panel.

  Architecture (desktop)
  ──────────────────────
  ┌────────────┬─────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────┐
  │  RAIL      │  CARD GRID (12 categories)      │  FEATURED PROMOS  │
  │  Sidebar   │  Icon · Title · Description     │  Hero · Bestseller│
  │  7 items   │  Hover: lift + border + arrow   │  Gradient CTAs    │
  └────────────┴─────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────┘

  Every top-level Hauptmenü item opens the *same* panel — categories
  never disappear or reflow when the visitor moves between top-level
  items, which is the layout-stability rule for SaaS-grade nav.

  Self-contained: ships its own CSS (scoped to .kx-mm) and SVG icons.

  @param {string} _root - Theme root URL prefix, e.g. '/' or '/de/'.
  @param {object} [parent_link] - Hovered top-level link (accepted for
    API compatibility; panel content is identical for every item).
  @param {string} [mode] - 'desktop' (default) | 'mobile'.
{%- enddoc -%}

{%- liquid
  assign mode = mode | default: 'desktop'

  if _root == blank
    assign _root = routes.root_url | default: '/'
  endif
  unless _root == '/'
    assign _root_check = _root | slice: -1, 1
    unless _root_check == '/'
      assign _root = _root | append: '/'
    endunless
  endunless
-%}

